{
  "events": [
    {
      "offset_seconds": 0,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0,
      "description": "Session starts with student 'Eddy' and tutor 'Varaun Gandhi' on screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 3.8,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Trying to figure out how to move my screen out of the way.",
      "speaker_name": "Eddy"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 19.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, do you mind sharing your screen as well?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 29,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 0,
      "description": "Student starts sharing screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 32,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "from_app": "Zoom",
      "to_app": "Chrome",
      "to_window": "MobyMax",
      "details": "Screen share displays MobyMax login screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 39,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Perfect. So you can start with it and if you have any questions, you know, you can raise your hand and I'll be here.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 48,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0,
      "description": "Student camera feed changes; a different student (Takoda) appears wearing a blue shirt.",
      "details": "Zoom label updates to 'takoda'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 50,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 52,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Hey! How are you?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 54,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 56,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you share your screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 59,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 101,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you share your screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 103,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 105,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "Uh no, why did [inaudible]",
      "speaker_name": "Classmate"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 115,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "from_app": "Zoom",
      "to_app": "Zoom",
      "to_window": "Sharing selection",
      "details": "Student shares the Zoom window initially."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 118,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Good?",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 119,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah. Now move on to MobyMax.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 122,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 123,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "from_app": "Zoom",
      "to_app": "Chrome",
      "to_window": "New Tab",
      "details": "Student opens a new tab."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 127,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Clever bookmark",
      "details": "Student clicks the Clever bookmark on the new tab page."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 129,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Zoom popup appears asking for permissions.",
      "details": "Popup: 'app.zoom.us wants to enter picture-in-picture automatically...'"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 130,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Allow this time button",
      "details": "Student clicks 'Allow this time' on the popup."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 135,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "So everybody should be going now...",
      "speaker_name": "Teacher"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 137,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "MobyMax icon",
      "details": "Student selects MobyMax from the Clever portal."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 140,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 10,
      "description": "Clever logging in screen transitions to MobyMax.",
      "details": "Loading animation visible."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 152,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I'm on MobyMax.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 154,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 156,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "[inaudible] talking to you?",
      "speaker_name": "Classmate"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 218,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 220,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay, so now you can start with the assignment assigned for today.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 224,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Assignments icon",
      "details": "Student clicks the 'Assigned' tab (book icon) in MobyMax."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 225,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Assigned?",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 230,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I don't have any assignments.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 233,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay, you can go to subjects.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 235,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 236,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Subjects tab",
      "details": "Student clicks the 'Subjects' tab."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 237,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Math icon",
      "details": "Student clicks the green 'Math' button."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 240,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "description": "MobyMax math module loads.",
      "details": "Loading spinner, then shows a starry background with a bunny."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 244,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I'm in.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 246,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Green arrow button",
      "details": "Student clicks the next/start arrow."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 248,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Lesson item",
      "details": "Student clicks 'Add within 1,000 using place value charts (no regrouping)'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 249,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Says 'Add within 1,000 using place value charts, no regrouping'.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 253,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Green arrow button",
      "details": "Student clicks the arrow to start the lesson."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 255,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay, you can continue with it and if you have any questions, you know, you can raise your hand and I'll be here.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 262,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "Takoda"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 301,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Ones column input",
      "details": "Student clicks the box under the ones column."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 302,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "9",
      "details": "Student types 9 in the ones place."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 304,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Tens column input",
      "details": "Student clicks the box under the tens column."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 305,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "7",
      "details": "Student types 7 in the tens place."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 307,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Hundreds column input",
      "details": "Student clicks the box under the hundreds column."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 308,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "5",
      "details": "Student types 5 in the hundreds place."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 310,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0,
      "description": "Student camera feed changes; a new student (Lester) appears wearing a red hat.",
      "details": "Zoom label updates to 'lester'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 312,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Hey Lester, how are you?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 315,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "How are you doing today?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 320,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I can't hear you.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 322,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't hear you. There's some issue with your headphones.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 327,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Student taps his headset microphone."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 329,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you hear me now?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 333,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Can you hear me?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 336,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 338,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you share your screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 340,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I can't hear you.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 343,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't hear you. There's some issue with your headphones.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 349,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you hear me now?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 351,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 352,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you share your screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 355,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Who me?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 356,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 400,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I can't hear you.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 406,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "There's something wrong with your headphones.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 418,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you still hear me?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 422,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 424,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I'm unable to hear you Lester.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 427,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Hang on.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 440,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I want you to share your screen now.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 444,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 445,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I want you to share your screen.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 448,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "My screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 449,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 450,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Am I?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 454,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 503,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Which one do I...",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 505,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't see your screen.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 513,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you call the professor again?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 522,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, can you call the teacher?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 534,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Teacher (Ms. Beeler) walks up behind the student.",
      "details": "She leans in to help."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 537,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "What are we not doing?",
      "speaker_name": "Ms. Beeler"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 540,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I'm trying to get in MobyMax.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 543,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "Well look...",
      "speaker_name": "Ms. Beeler"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 546,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "There you go, share.",
      "speaker_name": "Ms. Beeler"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 548,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 549,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "Is it sharing?",
      "speaker_name": "Ms. Beeler"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 552,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "You did?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 555,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't see it.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 558,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't see your screen.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 604,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, can you call the professor again?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 609,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, can you call the teacher?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 613,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 15,
      "description": "Student raises his hand to call the teacher."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 629,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Teacher returns to the student."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 633,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "And can you also tell her that there's some issue with your mic?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"
    },
    {
